{"tid":2186590,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"原來仲未完》中國汛情持續　緊急轉移安置近470萬人為近年最多","createTime":"2020-09-03T05:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T06:27:56.000Z","uid":13663,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3c98f953d0164b61656a28c7f5f88f2e74596d08","tid":2186590,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:22:40.000Z","msg":"內地汛情持續　緊急轉移安置近470萬人為近年最多<br />\n5分鐘前  Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】內地汛情持續，全國有超過七千萬人受災。<br />\n<br />\n應急管理部指，今年雨季汛情多年罕見，災害較為嚴重，全國有751條河流發生超警戒水位以上洪水，超過七千萬人受災，當中250萬人屬貧困人口，較近五年同期平均升一成七。<br />\n<br />\n271人因災死亡或失蹤；七萬間房屋倒塌，數字都較近五年少約五成。緊急轉移安置近470萬人，為近年最多。經濟損失超過兩千一百多億元人民幣，中央已累計下撥25億元支援災後重建，而目前仍處於主汛期，預期秋季汛情仍然嚴峻。<br />\n<br />\n國家防汛抗旱總指揮部辦公室主任李坤剛：「今年的秋汛形勢總體看，絕不可小視，不可有絲毫的懈怠。從歷史規律來看，進入秋季之後，我國西南、西北等一些省份降雨連連，往往導致嘉陵江、漢江、渭河等河流發生秋季洪水。從預測預報情況來看，今年秋季華西秋雨開始時間較常年偏早，雨量總體偏多。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=404159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404159&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hYMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=b602606e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404159&h=af782661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=404159</a>"},{"pid":"2baf1db1ccf0ef9be18e2d4bbd19a748b4c29220","tid":2186590,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/888777_maiko/status/1300449960740057088?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F888777_maiko%2Fstatus%2F1300449960740057088%3Fs%3D21&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hYMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=522e7b33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F888777_maiko%2Fstatus%2F1300449960740057088%3Fs%3D21&h=a4910b88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/888777_maiko/status/1300449960740057088?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日可以游水"},{"pid":"04fb991a71b1b930bbae7af388aa92468ac7f5a1","tid":2186590,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"中國有14億<del>人</del>韭菜，受災人數一億人都唔夠，中共又贏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41d38f6ed06b0dae48878c893114d7087c57db8","tid":2186590,"uid":8858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DapsDs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DapsDs.jpg&h=72568326&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d286059309a74475600737678d0ceac8e5e4fa0","tid":2186590,"uid":135409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:28:16.000Z","msg":"溫馨提示：<br />\n中國有十四億人口"},{"pid":"d94544e571dc954a62ea912f3ffbd8936cfa9e1d","tid":2186590,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:30:16.000Z","msg":"水唔退 - 人民生產活動繼續停止<br />\n水一退 - 瘟疫開始<br />\n<br />\n俾你有電子支付，全智能化生活又點<br />\n基建去水唔搞好，一場水災足夠將你打回原始社會"},{"pid":"867253cae34b0becb8b8248a1b4b22930bcf28ce","tid":2186590,"uid":153239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d94544e571dc954a62ea912f3ffbd8936cfa9e1d","tid":2186590,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:30:16.000Z","msg":"水唔退 - 人民生產活動繼續停止<br />\n水一退 - 瘟疫開始<br />\n<br />\n俾你有電子支付，全智能化生活又點<br />\n基建去水唔搞好，一場水災足夠將你打回原始社會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:32:33.000Z","msg":"假渠假城市<br />\n經濟大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c508d729ca05d161e4d0849de571bb9888c737a9","tid":2186590,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:35:38.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\"